    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "DATE: September 18, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, Philadelphia",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING OBJECT REPORTED OVER PHILADELPHIA",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "AUGUST 6, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "SABOTAGE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Remytel August 7 last.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Philadelphia, who is employed",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "by the [REDACTED] Phila-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "delphia, advised as follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Between 10:30 and 10:45 p.m. on August 6, 1947, she was sitting on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "the steps of her home with [REDACTED] She was facing north and observed",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "a large white object traveling at a very fast rate of speed to the south.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "There was a buzzing sound, not too loud but plainly audible, just after this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "object passed through the air. This white object left in its trail a thin",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "streak of smoke, which was grayish in color.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Miss [REDACTED] Philadelphia, who is em-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "ployed by the [REDACTED] INC.,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Philadelphia, stated she was sitting on the steps of [REDACTED] home on",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "the evening of August 6, 1947, around 10:45 p.m. engaging in conversation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "with [REDACTED] when [REDACTED] abruptly stopped in the middle of her con-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "versation and appeared to be frightened. [REDACTED] at that time was sitting",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "in a position in which she was facing south. She did not see any object in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "the sky after noting [REDACTED] change of expression, but she did hear a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "slight buzzing sound.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Philadelphia, an insurance agent,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "who was a former pilot of B-24's in the Army Air Corps, advised as follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "He was sitting on the steps of his home around 10:45 p.m. on August",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "6, 1947, with his wife; and his neighbors, the [REDACTED] family, were sitting on",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "their steps next door to the residence of [REDACTED] All of the above parties",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "were facing east. [REDACTED] noticed at this time an object, emitting a bluish-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "white flame, passing quickly through the air. The object was traveling from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "northeast to southwest. Using his experience in the Army Air Corps as a guide,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "[REDACTED] estimated the above object was between 1000 and 3000 feet in the air",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "and traveling at a rate of between 400 to 500 miles an hour. This object did",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "not lose elevation as it passed through the air and left either smoke or a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "condensation trail in its former path, which lasted for about two seconds.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "A hissing sound accompanied the passing of this object. This sound was moder-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "ate and not nearly as loud as the noise accompanying the passage of a rocket",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "ship.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "status": "blank"
    },
